foods.description: CRISPY BREADED CALAMARI SEASONED WITH SEA SALT & PEPPER WITH MARINARA SAUCE
foods.lowercaseDescription: crispy breaded calamari seasoned with sea salt & pepper with marinara sauce
foods.ingredients: CALAMARI (UROTEUTHIS DUVAUCELI), BLEACHED WHEAT FLOUR, VEGETABLE OIL (CONTAINS ONE OR MORE OF THE FOLLOWING: SOYBEAN, CORN AND/OR COTTONSEED OIL), WATER, MODIFIED CORN STARCH, CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: SEA SALT, BLACK PEPPER, WHEAT FLOUR, YELLOW CORN FLOUR, SUGAR, SALT, ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (FLOUR, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), RICE FLOUR, DEXTROSE, DRIED YEAST, LEAVENING (SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, SODIUM BICARBONATE, MONOCALCIUM PHOSPHATE, CALCIUM SULFATE), SPICES, MALTODEXTRIN, DRIED EGG WHITES, CORN STARCH, DRIED ONION, SODIUM CARBONATE, SODIUM CITRATE, MALIC ACID, NONFAT DRY MILK. MARINARA SAUCE: TOMATOES, WATER, TOMATO PASTE, PARMESAN CHEESE (PASTEURIZED PART-SKIM MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), GARLIC PUREE (FRESH GARLIC, CITRIC ACID), SALT, OLIVE OIL, SPICES, GARLIC POWDER, SUGAR, ONION POWDER, SODIUM BENZOATE, POTASSIUM SORBATE, ASCORBIC ACID.
